section.section:
The remedy or consequence may take the form of:
Reduction of the defaulting member's membership interest in the limited liability company;
Subordination of the defaulting member's membership interest in the limited liability company to that of the nondefaulting members;
A forced sale of the defaulting member's membership interest in the limited liability company;
Forfeiture of the defaulting member's membership interest in the limited liability company;
A loan by the nondefaulting members of the amount necessary to meet the commitment;
A determination of the value of the member's membership interest in the limited liability company by appraisal or by formula and redemption and sale of the defaulting member's membership interest in the limited liability company at that value; or
Any other remedy or consequences.
